    "body": "I met the same issue, but setting directory.truncate_to_repo to false does not work. Removeing all $git_branch$git_status$git_state in format works, but it disables git function in starship completely. \n\nI tried creating a empty git repo, the speed is still slow. \n\nI also tried switching from pwsh to nushell, nothing changed. ",
